According to his statement, he was supposed to look for guesthouses and restaurants.
In them he applied for bills for his consumption, according to whose model invoices were then produced in public competitions written by the Ministry of Youth and Sport, Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs and the Self-administration of the Capital City.
István Lados was mostly exhibiting invoices with his companion András ©rim, who, according to our information, most often wrote the reports needed to obtain subsidies.
